                            <comment id="254695" author="adilger" created="Sat, 14 Sep 2019 06:46:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;d rather that the default signalspec was EXIT, since that seems to be the only signal that we use anyway:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
stack_trap()
{       
        local arg=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
        local sigspec=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;${2:-EXIT}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That way it would only need to be specified if it was some other signal.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
